{"layout":"timeline","root":{"data":{"text":"<p><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;\">实用青年心理学</strong></p>","richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"456e3ffd-4b47-4bae-8152-2731227099d0"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 18px;\">第四章_应对策略</span></p>","uid":"1f6e5a61-1d3a-4284-bf08-322333a6d75c","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"\n      color: #749336;\n      font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: noraml;\n      font-style: normal;\n      text-decoration: none\n    \">应对的概念</span></p>","generalization":null,"richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"da6029ad-3292-41ec-a393-5decfbdd23c5"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">什么是应对：处理压力而做出的努力</span></p>","richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"6fad481f-e5ff-47b5-85d5-89d073c89195"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">应对的四种分组</span></p>","richText":true,"expand":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"88ccd6fc-fad8-4d5c-9a86-8e3ffd10a7f3","generalization":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">？不理解</span></p>","expand":true,"isActive":false,"richText":true}},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">问题聚焦和情绪聚焦的应对</span></p>","uid":"85b85c06-0bee-4c43-8682-4ed0cd0cbaef","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">卷入式应对和剥离式应对</span></p>","uid":"95b35d87-dfb9-476d-a4cf-5e7402317b1b","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">意义聚焦的应对</span></p>","uid":"10381395-0783-41ab-8aca-2e3342bb650a","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">前瞻式应对</span></p>","uid":"cf78edd7-8cb8-4ecd-b7b4-1496076d0130","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">应对的关键：最具适应意义的方法是灵活使用多种应对策略</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"6d8a1f74-70e5-42a0-bd81-eb3731e9e579"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 18px;\">价值有限的应对</span></p>","uid":"1fabae08-fc79-4dcd-b61d-8cc0f3069b6b","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">放弃</span></p>","uid":"b2bc2a2c-9029-4a3f-969e-133f2f21be11","expand":false,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"generalization":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">目标调整的关键是：正确的自我认知</span></p>","expand":true,"isActive":false,"richText":true}},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">放弃的形成机理：习得性无助，即因为没有能力处理不可避免的厌恶事件而产生的消极行为</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"5dc0a6ab-1ce1-4967-bf95-fe4616645f23","note":"进一步理解：\n对于厌恶事件的认知和解释决定了人们是否会产生习得性无助。具体来说，当人们开始相信事件超出了他们的掌控时，就会出现习得性无助。               "},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">放弃也有积极一面：当你被指派去做一份自己没有能力应付的工作时，那么与面对持续的压力和自尊的降低相比，辞职可能是一种更好的选择</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"d0cb2fa2-6ba5-4a85-a70f-c7a5c2158600"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">对放弃的认知：放弃应该被称为目标调整，关键是人要对自己的局限性，能力和真正目标有着清晰的认知，避免追求不切实际的目标而产生的自我强加的压力，也要避免不做尝试的过于轻易的放弃。</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"9c9c15cf-6811-4e5a-8344-e8c6530711ab","note":"需要对自我有着清晰的认知\n"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">攻击</span></p>","uid":"c77d19e5-fc93-4893-a708-5fb3bb104eff","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">什么是攻击：意图在身体或言语上伤害别人的任何行为。咆哮，诅咒和侮辱比枪击和殴打常见</span></p>","uid":"04de5e4b-1110-4809-b595-3596cefec000","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">替代性攻击：个体无法对挫折的真正根源发泄愤怒的时候，很可能会将愤怒转嫁到替代对象上的现象</span></p>","uid":"83b5bef7-6862-40c3-ba8a-59e4a97b7844","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">攻击只有坏处，它不会缓和压力，宣泄情感。相反，它会激发更多的愤怒和攻击，而且会引发人际冲突，带来更多的压力。</span></p>","uid":"96e3a8cc-34f8-4f95-8ce4-8242036468ad","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">自我放纵</span></p>","uid":"22d66303-e9ef-45f2-910e-2766352bded1","expand":false,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">自我放纵的本质：替代性补偿。即:当你在某个领域不顺时，你可能会通过追求替代性满足来补偿自己</span></p>","uid":"ddfc307b-3d97-4e13-9879-89490fe06ec5","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">自我放纵的例子：网络成瘾</span></p>","uid":"10c657b8-0432-4434-8698-377cfe00d9e5","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"个体因在现实中不如意而选择在网上耗时空度，获得满足来补偿自己。因此，当其不能上网时会感到焦虑，抑郁和空虚。然而过多的上网会妨碍他们在工作，学习和家庭中的正常表现。这进一步提升他们对网络的依赖程度。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">自我放纵也有积极的一面：一份热巧克力圣代可能帮助你在经历重大的挫折后平静下来，自我放纵的关键是不能过分的放纵自己，需要把握好度。</span></p>","uid":"c2242890-de91-458c-84f9-a684fa7c4efa","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">自我放纵会引发矛盾的情感，因为一时的快感过后会出现后悔，自责等 其它价值有限的应对。</span></p>","uid":"e36d0253-9cae-40ec-97d1-f0ccc064621a","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">自责</span></p>","uid":"75618edc-c748-42fe-bb38-a19ce671e2d9","expand":false,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">表现形式</span></p>","uid":"d23eee69-bbb5-4323-941c-387ca9711acb","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">不合理的将失败归因于个人缺点</span></p>","uid":"7ee277a4-93f5-46b9-a7c0-95877b66a295","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">注意别人给予的消极反馈而忽视积极反馈</span></p>","uid":"9a3cd274-ef62-4a27-b722-9f0fc7cb1c47","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">对未来做过分悲观的预测</span></p>","uid":"0df9a316-c470-4190-a748-e1329c85a806","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">自责基本只有缺点，会给个体带来巨大的心理压力</span></p>","uid":"6541acad-4b50-47f8-b27b-539809a8da54","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">防御性应对</span></p>","uid":"3783210f-85e9-4df9-a216-918108fcb46e","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">防御性应对分为以下5类</span></p>","uid":"57e69273-a581-4e2f-a4ab-ff55ae240655","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">否认，拒绝承认难以面对的事实</span></p>","uid":"f2974e40-3510-4ab4-bed2-6712e4bf1709","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">幻想。在想象中实现意识或潜意识中的愿望和冲动</span></p>","uid":"a862ff8b-042e-400b-99fd-d7d0a2492251","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">理智化。以一种超然，抽象的方式看待并应对困难，从而抑制自己的情绪反应</span></p>","uid":"6884d4ae-f60c-480b-8ca8-4d3cd48ba5e9","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"例如：刚被诊断出绝症，时日无多的患者。试图了解这种疾病的所有知识和治疗细节\n"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">撤销。试图通过赎罪来抵消负罪感</span></p>","uid":"77acf0dc-507d-4108-896b-14b6b7253e02","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"女儿因辱骂妈妈感到自责，会在每次辱骂后称赞妈妈的外貌"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">过度补偿。通过专注或夸大受欢迎的特征来弥补真实或臆想的缺陷</span></p>","uid":"50e70dbe-5f30-43e5-a909-8d99daff425a","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"一个没有交到朋友的转校生把经历全部放在提高学习成绩上。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">防御性应对的机理：通过自我欺骗起作用。扭曲自己现实，使其看起来不那么有威胁性，从而达到舒缓压力的目的。</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"8f14fd4f-8531-4335-bd18-a64e8aa9aaa5"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">防御性需要辩证来看。极端的自我欺骗是有害的，轻度的错觉通常有益</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"bbbc2fa7-0526-4ea2-9a02-247ed2a30963","note":"极端的自我欺骗：\n首先，只是逃避，无法真正解决问题。\n其次，否认，幻想，撤销，过度补偿等只是一厢情愿式的思维，很可能收效胜微。\n最后，它会让人们失去及时处理问题的黄金时间。\n\n轻度的错觉：\n可以适当缓解心理压力，远离焦虑。但是需要把握好度。 \n\n这两者的关键是：\n能否认清真正问题，及时处理真正的问题。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">建设性的应对</span></p>","uid":"4aafb46f-5877-4948-9262-10bb78dd2c4e","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">建设性应对的关键</span></p>","uid":"fdfd7985-6800-4e16-a700-8a3095526499","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">首先要直面问题。他是与任务相关的，以行动为导向。</span></p>","uid":"0b24407a-0f4a-4395-aa0e-2e9ecf92eb9c","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">其次，它需要努力的应对，它是一个积极主动的过程</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"55c72049-f779-4f20-b3f5-863bf617f325"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">然后，它需要你能基于对自己所面对的压力情景和应对资源的合理而现实的评估。 以防止自我欺骗</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"0bbed697-29cb-44dc-b90c-eb422a8a01ae"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">然后，它还要求人们可以辨识和管理潜在而有害的压力情绪反应</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"98b64638-1acd-4205-9e02-267267a5b71b","note":"在处理压力的过程中可能会有其它潜在的压力，因此需要可以辨识和管理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">最后，它还要求人们可以一定程度上控制潜在有害的或破坏性的行为习惯，这需要一定的自我控制能力</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"5bc7473c-5e23-4ba3-b964-9d9c76a4cd70"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(116, 147, 54); font-size: 14px;\">建设性应对的分类</span></p>","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"uid":"4056ddc3-9291-4213-a8f3-8a4afdea7f28"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"theme":{"template":"avocado","config":{}},"view":{"transform":{"scaleX":0.8,"scaleY":0.8000000000000002,"shear":0,"rotate":0,"translateX":-397.78831168831425,"translateY":-536.7333333333336,"originX":0,"originY":0,"a":0.8,"b":0,"c":0,"d":0.8,"e":-397.78831168831425,"f":-536.7333333333336},"state":{"scale":0.8,"x":-397.78831168831425,"y":-536.7333333333336,"sx":-396.78831168831425,"sy":-496.73333333333363}}}